@WordApi_HostAddress = http://localhost:5269

### Approach A — parsed DocumentModel JSON
GET {{WordApi_HostAddress}}/api/document
Accept: application/json

### Approaches B/C/D — raw .docx bytes
GET {{WordApi_HostAddress}}/api/document/file
Accept: application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.wordprocessingml.document

